# Modern Scientific Calculator

## Internship Project

A GUI-based Modern Scientific Calculator developed using Python and Tkinter. This application performs both basic and scientific mathematical calculations with a simple and user-friendly interface.

## Project Overview

The Modern Scientific Calculator is designed to help users perform mathematical operations quickly and accurately. It includes basic arithmetic functions as well as scientific calculations such as trigonometric and logarithmic operations.

## Features

- Basic Arithmetic Operations (+, -, *, /)
- Square Root Calculation
- Square and Cube Functions
- Sin, Cos, and Tan Functions
- Log and Natural Log Functions
- Percentage Calculation
- Decimal Number Support
- Modern Dark Theme User Interface

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Tkinter
- Math Module
- Visual Studio Code

## Output

The calculator provides a modern dark-themed graphical user interface with colorful buttons and scientific calculation features.

## Learning Outcomes

- Python Programming
- GUI Development using Tkinter
- Event Handling
- Desktop Application Development

## Future Scope

- Add Calculator History
- Add Dark and Light Themes
- Add Advanced Scientific Functions
- Export Calculation Reports
- Develop Mobile Application Version

## Developer

Kajal Joshi

## Conclusion

This project helped in understanding Python GUI development and implementing scientific calculations in a desktop application using Tkinter.# Modern Scientific Calculator

